<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.8.6">
<l>āṉā yarumā ṉiraiyu maṅkoḻiyak</l>
<l>kūṉā yatōrkoṟ ṟavilloṉ ṟukaiyēntip</l>
<l>pōṉā riruntā raiyumpārt tuppukutīr</l>
<l>ēṉōr kaḷmuṉṉeṉ ṉituveṉ ṉituveṉṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When you left the cow herders and the herd there,</l>
<l>Bearing in hand a victorious bow which becomes bent,</l>
<l>Having watched who went and who stayed, you entered;</l>
<l>Why [right] in front of others? What is this? What is this?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
